---
---

<section id="servizi" class="py-14 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-warm-100">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

    <div class="text-center mb-12 sm:mb-16">
      <p class="text-brand text-xs sm:text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-3">Cosa facciamo</p>
      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-ink-900 text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-4 leading-snug">Le nostre divisioni</h2>
      <p class="text-ink-600 max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed text-base sm:text-lg">
        Tre aree di specializzazione, un unico standard: lavoro preciso, tempi certi, nessuna sorpresa.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5 sm:gap-6">

      <a
        href="/montaggi"
        class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 sm:p-8 shadow-[0_2px_12px_rgba(26,22,18,0.07)] hover:shadow-[0_10px_36px_rgba(26,22,18,0.13)] border border-warm-200 hover:border-brand/30 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 flex flex-col overflow-hidden"
      >
        <span class="absolute top-4 right-5 font-display font-black text-7xl text-warm-200 select-none leading-none pointer-events-none">01</span>

        <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-brand/10 group-hover:bg-brand rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 transition-colors duration-300 relative z-10">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-brand group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" aria-hidden="true">
            <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"></rect>
            <path d="M8 21h8M12 17v4"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <p class="text-brand text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] mb-2 relative z-10">Divisione</p>
        <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-ink-900 text-xl sm:text-2xl mb-3 leading-snug relative z-10">Montaggi</h3>
        <p class="text-ink-600 leading-relaxed text-base flex-1 relative z-10">
          Cucine complete, cabine armadio, librerie a parete, arredi su misura. Montaggi di pregio con la cura che meritano.
        </p>
        <span class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-brand font-semibold text-sm group-hover:gap-3 transition-all duration-200 relative z-10">
          Scopri i lavori
          <span class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-200 inline-block">→</span>
        </span>
      </a>

      <a
        href="/progettazione"
        class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 sm:p-8 shadow-[0_2px_12px_rgba(26,22,18,0.07)] hover:shadow-[0_10px_36px_rgba(26,22,18,0.13)] border border-warm-200 hover:border-brand/30 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 flex flex-col overflow-hidden"
      >
        <span class="absolute top-4 right-5 font-display font-black text-7xl text-warm-200 select-none leading-none pointer-events-none">02</span>

        <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-brand/10 group-hover:bg-brand rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 transition-colors duration-300 relative z-10">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-brand group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"></path>
            <path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <p class="text-brand text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] mb-2 relative z-10">Divisione</p>
        <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-ink-900 text-xl sm:text-2xl mb-3 leading-snug relative z-10">Progettazione</h3>
        <p class="text-ink-600 leading-relaxed text-base flex-1 relative z-10">
          Dalla prima consulenza alla consegna chiavi in mano: ogni passo del nostro processo, documentato con foto.
        </p>
        <span class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-brand font-semibold text-sm group-hover:gap-3 transition-all duration-200 relative z-10">
          Vedi come lavoriamo
          <span class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-200 inline-block">→</span>
        </span>
      </a>

      <a
        href="/contract"
        class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 sm:p-8 shadow-[0_2px_12px_rgba(26,22,18,0.07)] hover:shadow-[0_10px_36px_rgba(26,22,18,0.13)] border border-warm-200 hover:border-brand/30 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 flex flex-col overflow-hidden sm:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1"
      >
        <span class="absolute top-4 right-5 font-display font-black text-7xl text-warm-200 select-none leading-none pointer-events-none">03</span>

        <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-brand/10 group-hover:bg-brand rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 transition-colors duration-300 relative z-10">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-brand group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"></path>
            <polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <p class="text-brand text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] mb-2 relative z-10">Divisione</p>
        <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-ink-900 text-xl sm:text-2xl mb-3 leading-snug relative z-10">Contract</h3>
        <p class="text-ink-600 leading-relaxed text-base flex-1 relative z-10">
          Arredo completo per hotel, uffici e grandi residenze. Numeri importanti, qualità che non scende mai.
        </p>
        <span class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-brand font-semibold text-sm group-hover:gap-3 transition-all duration-200 relative z-10">
          Scopri i grandi lavori
          <span class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-200 inline-block">→</span>
        </span>
      </a>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>
